 puzzles and a fully featured editor to make your own. Submit them for inclusion in future user packs!\n\nThere are six premium-themed puzzle packs available to purchase for a total of over 200 puzzles.\n\nFeatures\n - 200+ puzzles, ranging from trivial to taxing\n - Hints for when you get stuck\n - Fully featured puzzle creator mode\n - 7 visual themes to suit all tastes\n - Fully adjustable settings\n - Personal puzzle statistics\n - Over 25 achievements\n - Meta leaderboards for each puzzle\n - In-game store for extra packs and hints  \n\nJoin the Discord!\nhttps://discord.gg/VmA5fWPryw\n", "short_description": "Meet Arthur Owl and his clever game Word Block. With around 100 included puzzles and even more in downloadable packs, you'll have plenty to do!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://deeperbeige.com/files/PrivacyPolicy_TOS.pdf", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Deeperbeige Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://deeperbeige.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "377978390272490"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "923467478661540"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "740728558007830"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "740728558007830"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1710365280, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "740728558007830"}]}, "liv